content:
Use account and contact reports to learn about active, neglected, or new accounts, as well as accounts by account owner or partner. The two standard contact reports let you create a mailing list of contacts or track opportunities by contact role.

Standard Report: Field History - report on field history on accounts or contacts if your organization tracks it.
Standard Report: Person Accounts - include fields specific to person accounts in account and contact reports if used.
Mass Mail Merge - export contact data, do a mass mail merge using Microsoft Word.
View Filter for Account Reports - limit account data by options such as My accounts, My account team accounts, etc.

Activity Reports
title: Creating and Managing Salesforce Account and Contact Reports
